<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,406,1854,1880]" italics="true" pageId="34" pageNumber="35">Leptodactylus riveroi</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Heyer, W. R. &amp; Pyburn, W. F." box="[413,686,1854,1880]" pageId="34" pageNumber="35" pagination="560 - 566" refId="ref35246" refString="Heyer, W. R. &amp; Pyburn, W. F. (1983) Leptodactylus riveroi, a new frog species from Amazonia, South America (Anura: Leptodactylidae). Proceedings of the Biological Society of Washington, 96, 560 - 566." type="journal article" year="1983">Heyer et Pyburn 1983</bibRefCitation>
